debris = game:GetService("Debris")
-- finds direction to point compass at for rare egg
function findNearestRareEgg(pos) local temp = nil local rareEgg = nil local list = game.Workspace:FindFirstChild("eggroot")
if list ~= nil then list = list:GetChildren() for x = 1, #list do local temp = list[x] eggNum = eggNameToRarity(temp.Name) if rareEgg == nil then rareEgg = temp elseif eggNum > eggNameToRarity(rareEgg.Name) then rareEgg = temp elseif eggNum == eggNameToRarity(rareEgg.Name) then rareEgg = closerEgg(rareEgg,temp) end end end return rareEgg end
function closerEgg(rareEgg, temp)
local rareEggPos = rareEgg.Handle.Position local tempEggPos = temp.Handle.Position
local humanPos = script.Parent.Torso.Position
if math.abs((rareEggPos - humanPos).magnitude) > math.abs((tempEggPos - humanPos).magnitude) then return temp end
return rareEgg
end
function eggNameToRarity(eggName)
local rarity = 0
local eggNum = tonumber(eggName)
if eggNum == 1 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 2 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 3 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 4 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 5 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 6 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 7 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 8 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 9 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 10 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 11 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 12 then rarity = 2 elseif eggNum == 13 then rarity = 2 elseif eggNum == 14 then rarity = 3 elseif eggNum == 15 then rarity = 4 elseif eggNum == 16 then rarity = 5 elseif eggNum == 18 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 19 then rarity = 2 elseif eggNum == 20 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 21 then rarity = 0 elseif eggNum == 22 then rarity = 1 elseif eggNum == 23 then rarity = 6 elseif eggNum == 24 then rarity = 7 end
return rarity
end

if closeRareEgg ~= nil then
local pointDirection = nil
